{"tid":1281032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急 - 請暫時修改社交媒體設定】","createTime":"2019-07-03T07:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T07:40:10.000Z","uid":263409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"26801a9b0415e07f16663700838c8a0527bfc791","tid":1281032,"uid":263409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:13:42.000Z","msg":"【緊急 - 請暫時修改社交媒體設定】<br />\n<br />\n剛被我們協助現正回家的朋友表示，對方正大規模查看大家曾 like 或 share 的所有有關帖文。若有任何朋友感到不安，不希望被別人得知 like 或 share 過的任何帖文，可將相關 社交媒體（facebook, instagram等）的貼文、相片或整個戶口的私隱設定為不公開閱覽，又或可暫時 deactivate (請保留通訊渠道免產生失聯之誤會) ; 如有需要，FB messenger 可繼續保留作溝通之用）。請大家留意及廣傳此訊息。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 星火同盟 抗爭支援 facebook <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2F&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaVw%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=b73a8b5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/</a>"},{"pid":"b83f0fdb3f5e03e6b4533eda0e8d973ed52746a5","tid":1281032,"uid":263409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:23:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0025b1941a508f0ba41d75327aabcf161b875711","tid":1281032,"uid":263409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:28:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8fc2a4bd53d2888e9d8e0ce022f9ed632d24955","tid":1281032,"uid":263409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:40:10.000Z","msg":"推"}]}